title: Number of Incorporations for United States
notes:
Hawaii Incorporations Are Included Beginning With 1958. Alaska Incorporations Are Included Beginning With 1960. District Of Columbia Incorporations Are Included Beginning With 1963. Source: For 1945-1957 Data: Dun'S Statistical Review; For 1958-1969 Data: Business Trend, Monthly New Incorporations

This NBER data series m10090 appears on the NBER website in Chapter 10 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter10.html.
